events.name: Dream Fairy(1st Version)
events.note: <Alert> <Block Vision Regions: 4> <Alert Range: 5> <Alert FOV angle: 160> <Encounter Direction Lock> <Random Move Weight: 0.3> <Always Update Movement> <Save Event Location>

parameters: Spawn Event: Spawn At X, Y
You can see somebody trapped in the mirror.
It's a shadowy woman with a long neck and witch hat.
Her smile looks blissful, even contagious.
You can feel a cold hand grasping at the recess of your mind.
Suddenly, you feel yourself standing before an endless void of numbers.
You sense an immensely powerful presence at the heart of the Spider Forest!
A shattering noise was heard, but the mirror is still intact.
You can feel blood coming out of your ears.
